HEADWORD: Partitive
<hw>Par"ti*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>partitif</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Gram.)</fld> <def>Denoting a part;
