==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Partitive
<hw>Par"ti*tive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Gram.)</fld> <def>A word or
phrase expressing partition, or denoting a part; <as>as, the phrase
⟦ldquo⟧of the team⟦rdquo⟧ in ⟦ldquo⟧half of the
team⟦rdquo⟧</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Partitively</ent>⟦br⟧
